{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_51_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 こころが主役のこころのための日",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私にこころの『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』\nの企画を手伝ってほしい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y‚ you need my help to plan\nKokoro's 'Miracle☆Idol Birthday!'?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.0845355671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　任せて下さい！　こころに最高の誕生日を\nプレゼントしたい気持ちはスタッフさん達と一緒です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Leave it to me! I want to present Kokoro the best birthday\njust like how the staff want!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.0333326976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "こころがやりたいことを全力で叶えます！！\nん？　私が考えるこころのやりたいこと……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll do my best to make Kokoro's wishes come true!!\nHuh? You mean what I think Kokoro wants to do……?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……多分リズノワで何かしたいって\n言うと思うので、莉央さんと葵さんの予定を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…… She’ll probably say she wants to do something with LizNoir‚\nso I should check Rio-san and Aoi-san’s schedules……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6619723957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.7786382993
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.7786382993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ということで！　こころは誕生日に何がしたい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So! What do you want to do for your birthday‚ Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8286382993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.7482538701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ！　いよいよ待ちに待った誕生日！！\nこころが主役のこころのための日！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oooh! It’s finally my long-awaited birthday!!\nThe day for Kokoro‚ starring Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7815872034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "愛がスタッフさんをお手伝いしてる……のはちょっと\n不安だけど……しっかり盛り上げて、盛大に祝ってね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai’s helping the staff…… That makes me\na little nervous…… but please make sure to liven things up and celebrate it in style!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7815872034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.2482538701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫だよ～！　今回は事前準備だって\nしっかり……えっと、なんでもない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Of course~! This time‚ I’ve even taken care of preparations beforehand…\nfor this time… Um‚ never mind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.3759658021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "自らハードルを上げていくスタイル！\nいいねいいね～！　期待してるよ、愛！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are raising the bar yourself!\nGood‚ good~! I’m looking forward to it‚ Ai!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1092991354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.0426337403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ところでこの企画って誰と何をやるかまでこころが\n決められるんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ for this plan‚ I get to decide\nwho to do it with and what to do‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9093004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.5093004069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……誕生日の人が決められるよ！\nでも誰とやるかは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah…… The birthday girl gets to decide!\nBut who to do it with is……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.799998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.8559954168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあメンバーは、愛とすずにゃんで\nよろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ then I’d like Ai and Suzunya to\nHelp me~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3559954168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.4893287501
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ？　莉央さんと葵さんじゃなくていいの！？\nこころはてっきりリズノワで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh? You’re okay with it not being Rio-san and Aoi-san!?\nI thought you would definitely want them……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9333377838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.422571389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに慌ててどうしたの？\n別に……先輩達からはいつでもお祝いしてもらえるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you so flustered about?\nIt’s no big deal…… I can always get congratulations from the seniors",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4892380556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.522571389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、二人とも最近すっごく忙しそうだよね？　昨日\nなんて収録の合間に莉央さんソファーで爆睡だったよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "besides‚ they both seem really busy lately‚ don’t they? Yesterday‚\nRio-san was fast asleep on the sofa during a break between recording sessions~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0559047223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、せっかくだし他のメンバーにしようかなって！\n企画意図的にもそっちの方が良くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I thought I’d take this opportunity to do something with other members!\nThat fits the plan better‚ don’t you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6892411074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.8225718976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ずーっと前からすずにゃんと愛と\nやりたいことがあったんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I’ve always wanted\nto do something with Suzunya and Ai~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4892385643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 120.0892385643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "確かに違うグループから選んでいる人が\n多いかもだけど……。私達とやりたいこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that a lot of people choose\nmembers from different groups… then what's something you want to do with us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5990622863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.9195978643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　それは……まだ莉央さんも葵さんも\n持ったことのない冠番組！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! It's something… even Rio-san and Aoi-san haven't achieved‚\nwhich is a TV show named after us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8529311976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 134.0195978643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "この機会にリズノワ初の冠番組をゲットして\nリズノワの人気を鰻登りにする作戦！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to use this opportunity to get LizNoir's first own TV show‚\nand make LizNoir’s popularity skyrocket!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.386264531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.6195978643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "どうかな？　もちろん、最初はこころ一人でやるけど\nゆくゆくはリズノワのコーナーも作る予定だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How does that sound? Of course‚ I’ll do it on my own at first‚\nBut eventually I’m going to create a LizNoir segment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6195978643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.7196009161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_51_01-ai010.m4a",
